name: Another Pathetic Lifeform
Lore: 'Young Obi-Wan has much to learn about the living Force. Patience with others is also high on that list.',
Text: 'Deploy on table. Once during each of opponent''s turns, if you occupy a battleground site, may activate 1 Force. While opponent has a nonunique alien or non-unique starfighter in battle, opponent may not draw more than two battle destiny. (Immune to Alter.)',
